100â†’	 * @param normalVec  The unit vector (normalized vector) from the location of the source ball to the location of the target ball.
101â†’	 * @param minSeparation The minimum allowed non-colliding separation between the centers of the balls = maximum allowed colliding separation.
102â†’	 * @param distance The actual distance between the centers of the balls.
103â†’	 * @return A Point object which is the amount to "nudge" the source ball away from the target ball.
